snippet.textDisplay: ZHC I've been watching your vids for some time now and you do awesome stuff, however, please (constructive criticism) learn how to spray paint with a can. I took 4 years of autobody and watching you do anything with a spray can is cringy. Your work could be so much better if you had proper technique. As far as the lambo goes, I think taking it to an autobody shop to be cleared would have been a better idea. The art will last longer. Also think that over time that small clear job you did will not hold and the art will not look good as time goes on. Just my advice, keep going, and keep getting better.
